HEADWORD: glasscutter
<hw>glasscutter</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>one who cuts or
grinds designs on glass.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>one who cuts flat glass to size.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> glassworker, glazier, glazer.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>glazed</ent>⟦br⟧
